{"tid":1578888,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無社交媒體市民保護連儂牆被打 事後住宅被淋火水 懷疑警察洩露個人資料","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T14:33:29.000Z","uid":22556,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"99d4e2acdd32d6028d0a4f0b3caeac488680f320","tid":1578888,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）上星期六（9月14日），大批中年人士於各區連儂牆拆除文宣，引起反送中的市民不滿，其中在將軍澳文曲里公園附近更演變肢體衝突，至少三名市民遭到襲擊。有受襲市民批評行動「清潔為名，打人為實」，今早在新民主同盟陪同下，到將軍澳警署請願，要求警方嚴肅跟進案件，加強警力保護市民安全。<br />\n<br />\n遇襲的譚先生身穿醫院病人服到場，他指在景林邨少女遭刀手襲擊後，自己就一直在區內巡視連儂牆，希望當有危險時可以及時疏散途人。譚先生表示，當日有近30人清理區內的連儂牆，並得悉有兩名市民遇襲受傷，故立即趕到文曲里隧道現場。他指自己當時只是呼喊了一句「啲學生做得咁靚，你哋拆咗佢，有冇良心？」後，便被三、四人追打及圍毆近半分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n譚先生指警方在事發後近25分鐘才到場，有市民更向警方提供相關人士的照片，但警方仍一口咬定案件難以追查，更諷刺他被打時間短促，「20、30秒咋」。譚先生認為，文曲里公園及香港單車館外均有多個閉路電視，「冇可能搵唔到佢地去向」，並質疑警方未有盡力調查，態度輕率。<br />\n<br />\n在案發當晚，譚先生的住所亦被人「淋火水」，他強調自己一直有保護個人資料，「冇Facebook、冇IG」，亦未有向人透露住址，質疑警方洩露其個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n他向記者展示手部及臉部傷勢，又指頭部紅腫及視覺出現重影，仍在留醫階段，批評施襲人士「清潔為名，打人為實」。他指傷勢嚴重影響日常生活，已四日沒有上班，只能進食流質食物，甚至不敢回家。<br />\n<br />\n對於星期六全港各區將再有「清潔行動」，譚先生表明會繼續現身，更建議各區街坊組成人鏈守護自己的連儂牆，「你哋咁辛苦嘅心血係唔應該每日被拆、每周被清」。他又指在連月巡視期間，從沒有見過一個有警察在區內巡守，反而要由街坊承受風險自發保護社區。<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟區議員鍾錦麟表示，警方的處理案件的手法令人擔憂，令市民擔心警方未有認真跟進，變相縱容向連儂牆的市民施襲，甚至在星期六會發生更大規模的衝突，要求警方嚴肅跟進案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067316&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj4jsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=ee0eccbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067316&h=798113f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067316</a>"},{"pid":"e75a7650df2cec58696636c80689dc2b4a947532","tid":1578888,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f97701284ec87037a416ff827d4e57ac42f4ded","tid":1578888,"uid":71210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e1a4e917840d962ca1d7824f75dd0087af4a1b","tid":1578888,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf882708201acb1beaf67bbc81d3fdf687b870a","tid":1578888,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:24:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7d600d7bfa0e32114aa6acb5e37e772c463a340","tid":1578888,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:24:30.000Z","msg":"煲大佢"},{"pid":"23376f86f182feab7f73eb7e0c091d2b33565c6b","tid":1578888,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cb5945417ff80bbe4c49ff679107e5cf0cbd0d","tid":1578888,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"仲信狗?"},{"pid":"41fbf1fa0316ed7e928b0107415d1dc6e0266598","tid":1578888,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"直情係休班警做啦 死仆街"},{"pid":"c5bcc65c2e9836ec36283a0c578a52a959666c9a","tid":1578888,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"死警狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc560ac88a10ffd122110c22c1d189d9725a93d","tid":1578888,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲靠班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔仆返你二下拉你返去<br />\n我覺得已經要覺得好彩<br />\n<br />\n今時今日班狗就係殺人犯同黑社會，去找呢啲人求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d053919eaa34df48745e9b438dced8ce870167d","tid":1578888,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢需唔需要支援?"},{"pid":"6f080d2453f5bd6e3a9c8f20db32743737b930d1","tid":1578888,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"[未知算唔算文宣/輸出革命]戰區分法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n小弟出post想請大家過目"},{"pid":"72d0d121d00bd9019e46ae0b2674489974f38ab8","tid":1578888,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d4e2acdd32d6028d0a4f0b3caeac488680f320","tid":1578888,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）上星期六（9月14日），大批中年人士於各區連儂牆拆除文宣，引起反送中的市民不滿，其中在將軍澳文曲里公園附近更演變肢體衝突，至少三名市民遭到襲擊。有受襲市民批評行動「清潔為名，打人為實」，今早在新民主同盟陪同下，到將軍澳警署請願，要求警方嚴肅跟進案件，加強警力保護市民安全。<br />\n<br />\n遇襲的譚先生身穿醫院病人服到場，他指在景林邨少女遭刀手襲擊後，自己就一直在